# CODEOWNERS
#
# Ownership rules for this monorepo. GitHub uses the LAST matching pattern.
# Order patterns broad -> specific so that specific paths override earlier globs.
#
# NOTE: You cannot assign an entire org as a code owner (e.g. @ElHackos-999 is invalid).
# To include "anyone from the org" create a team (e.g. @ElHackos-999/core) and add all members.
# For now we list explicit individual owners. Replace / extend with teams when they exist.
#
# Core maintainers:
#   @simon-tanna
#   @BenDavies1218
#   @marco-labrys
#
# Team naming suggestions (create these before swapping them in):
#   @ElHackos-999/core        -> broad fallback
#   @ElHackos-999/app         -> application (apps/nextjs)
#   @ElHackos-999/platform    -> build + tooling + generators
#   @ElHackos-999/frontend    -> UI components, validators, styling
#   @ElHackos-999/backend     -> api/auth/db packages
#   @ElHackos-999/data        -> database schema & migrations
#   @ElHackos-999/docs        -> documentation
#
# Fallback: everything not matched later.
* @simon-tanna @BenDavies1218 @marco-labrys

